original: ROSENDAHL,, Carl Theodor (Thore), Disponent, Trollhättan, f Sthlm 28/2 90 av bergsing G T R o Hanna R, gm Elsa Afzelius. Mog.ex Sthlm 08, civingex KTH (kemi) 11. Anst v Sthlms Superfosfatfabr AB:s verk v Månsbo 11—20 o v Trollhättan sed. 20. Styr.led i Trollhättans Elektrokem Arb.giv.frb fr 21, sekr, v. ordf o ordf i Trollhättans Ing.klubb 21— 34, 34—36 o 37—39, sekr i Trollhättans Rotary-klubb sed. 38. Resor: Engl 17 o 19, Engl, Canada, Hawaii, Jap o USA 35. Led av Sv Tekn.frn, Kemistsamf o Trollh Rotaryklubb. Hobbies: Filateli, foto, cykling, skidåkning.
translated: ROSENDAHL, Carl Theodor (Thore), Manager, Trollhättan, b. Stockholm 28/2 90, son of miner G T R and Hanna R, m. Elsa Afzelius. Graduated Stockholm 08, civil engineer degree from KTH (chemistry) 11. Employed at Stockholm Superphosphate Factory in Månsbo 11-20 and in Trollhättan since 20. Board member of Trollhättan Electrochemical Works Employees Association starting from 21, secretary, vice chairman and chairman of Trollhättan Engineering Club 21-34, 34-36 and 37-39, secretary of Trollhättan Rotary Club since 38. Travelled to England in 17 and 19, England, Canada, Hawaii, Japan and USA in 35. Member of Swedish Technical Society, Swedish Chemical Society, and Trollhättan Rotary Club. Hobbies: Philately, photography, cycling, skiing.
